data.description: ***LOCATION*LOCATION*LOCATION*** Home qualified for USDA Financing. Walk everywhere you need to be from this perfectly located, completely updated lovely home in the heart of Downtown Latrobe! Be just steps away from the elementary school, grocery store, restaurants, tanning/nail salon, walking trail and more.  This home was gutted & remodeled top to bottom in approx. 2005. Great floorplan, spacious rooms, absolutely amazing large private yard, covered front & back porches, big lovely sundeck! The basement is clean, dry & recently painted. The basement has a generously sized laundry area w/washer & dryer included, work shop, cold cellar, lots of room for gym, play or storage.  Home is completely move in ready, very attractive inside & out, beautiful landscaping & gardens in the back fenced yard. You will enjoy entertaining friends & family in this large, open, eat in kitchen. Upstairs bathroom is oversized and boasts a tub/shower combo.  -Hardwood Flooring throughout the home-
